data.description: Charming 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath pool home in a prime location in NW Tampa near everything you could ever possibly want! Conveniently located near shopping, dinning, Tampa International Airport, Raymond James Stadium, major highways and the Causeway for quick access to the beaches. No HOA or CDD. New AC in 2022, pavers in driveway and gazebo area in 2022, new pool pump in 2022, new roof in 2013. This home boasts a large 2 car garage with so much space for storage! Rustic charm throughout with the unique choice of ceramic tile and cozy fireplace in the living space. Quaint kitchen featuring an island and large pantry. Large room off the main bedroom with two skylights and half bath make it a great space for an office or exercise room. This house has SO much character! Not to mention a beautifully paved pool deck and entertainment space in the backyard fully fenced and adorned with palm trees for a tropical oasis vibe. You won't want to miss the opportunity to see this one!
